OL,3,CScotland becomes first UK nation to
OL,4,Cscreen babies for spinal muscular
OL,5,Catrophy
OL,7,FScotland has become the first part of
OL,8,Fthe UK to screen babies for spinal
OL,9,Fmuscular atrophy, a rare condition
OL,10,Fthat causes progressive muscle wastage.
OL,12,FThe condition can result in muscle
OL,13,Fweakness, breathing and swallowing
OL,14,Fissues and a loss of mobility in
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,17,FMany children diagnosed with spinal
OL,18,Fmuscular atrophy (SMA) will struggle
OL,19,Fto lift their head or walk.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
