FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774275077
OL,3,CScotland becomes first UK nation to
OL,4,Cscreen babies for spinal muscular
OL,5,Catrophy
OL,7,FIf caught early, the most devastating
OL,8,Feffects of the condition can be
OL,9,Favoided.
OL,11,FAll parents in Scotland - where an
OL,12,Faverage of three to four babies a year
OL,13,Fare born with SMA - will now be
OL,14,Foffered screening for their newborns
OL,15,Fthrough an existing blood spot test,
OL,16,Fwhich is taken around four days after
OL,17,Fbirth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
