FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774275077
OL,3,CScotland becomes first UK nation to
OL,4,Cscreen babies for spinal muscular
OL,5,Catrophy
OL,7,FTony and Carrie Pearson's daughter
OL,8,FGrayce was around six months old when
OL,9,Fshe stopped being able to move her
OL,10,Flegs and began losing her strength.
OL,12,FAfter several referrals, doctors in
OL,13,F2024 confirmed it was SMA type two.
OL,15,FSince then, the parents have been
OL,16,Fcampaigning for a national screening
OL,17,Fprogramme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774275077
OL,3,CScotland becomes first UK nation to
OL,4,Cscreen babies for spinal muscular
OL,5,Catrophy
OL,7,FCarrie said: "We wish it came out
OL,8,Fsooner, obviously, but we are grateful
OL,9,Fnow that every other child isn't going
OL,10,Fto go through all those issues.
OL,12,F"They're going to get treatment sooner
OL,13,Fand be able to meet their milestones,
OL,14,Fand all families aren't going to have
OL,15,Fto go through that anxiety and stress
OL,16,Fthat we did, and other families went
OL,17,Fthrough."
OL,26,@oD@NOUtD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
