OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774275077
OL,3,CScotland becomes first UK nation to
OL,4,Cscreen babies for spinal muscular
OL,5,Catrophy
OL,7,FShe said it was "only logical that the
OL,8,Frest of the UK falls behind" Scotland
OL,9,Fbefore adding: "Can you really put a
OL,10,Fprice on a child's life?"
OL,12,FTony said the pilot is "history being
OL,13,Fmade in Scotland". He went on: "It's
OL,14,F#4 to test a baby for SMA. Is a
OL,15,Fchild's life worth #4? Definitely."
