OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774275077
OL,3,CScotland becomes first UK nation to
OL,4,Cscreen babies for spinal muscular
OL,5,Catrophy
OL,7,FDr Sarah Smith, director of the
OL,8,Fscreening laboratory in Glasgow where
OL,9,Fall the tests will be conducted, said
OL,10,Fthe aim of the pilot was to reveal
OL,11,Fwhether a baby has SMA before they
OL,12,Fshowed any symptoms and before any
OL,13,Fmuscle wastage took place.
OL,15,FDr Smith said: "It will mean these
OL,16,Fbabies are picked up pre-
OL,17,Fsymptomatically.
OL,26,@wD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774275077
OL,3,CScotland becomes first UK nation to
OL,4,Cscreen babies for spinal muscular
OL,5,Catrophy
OL,7,F"With SMA, unfortunately, once the
OL,8,Fsymptoms are present, you can't easily
OL,9,Freverse them. Our aim is to stop the
OL,10,Fsymptoms from actually happening in
OL,11,Fthe first place."
OL,13,FFormer Little Mix star Jesy Nelson has
OL,14,Fcampaigned for all babies to be tested
OL,15,Ffor SMA, after disclosing her twins,
OL,16,FOcean Jade and Story Monroe Nelson-
OL,17,FFoster, were diagnosed with the rare
OL,18,Fcondition.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
