OL,3,CScotland becomes first UK nation to
OL,4,Cscreen babies for spinal muscular
OL,5,Catrophy
OL,7,FIn February, she announced she had
OL,8,Fbecome a patron of SMA UK and urged
OL,9,Fher fans to donate to the charity,
OL,10,Fwhich aims to improve the lives of
OL,11,Fpeople with the condition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
