OL,3,CScotland becomes first UK nation to
OL,4,Cscreen babies for spinal muscular
OL,5,Catrophy
OL,7,FIn an Instagram video post Nelson
OL,8,Fshared around the time of the
OL,9,Fdiagnosis, she said: "We were told
OL,10,Fthat they're probably never going to
OL,11,Fbe able to walk, they probably will
OL,12,Fnever regain their neck strength, so
OL,13,Fthey will be disabled, and so the best
OL,14,Fthing we can do right now is to get
OL,15,Fthem treatment, and then just hope for
OL,16,Fthe best."
OL,26,@qD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
