OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774275077
OL,3,CScotland becomes first UK nation to
OL,4,Cscreen babies for spinal muscular
OL,5,Catrophy
OL,7,FGiles Lomax, chief executive officer
OL,8,Fof SMA UK and the father of twins
OL,9,Fliving with SMA, said the Scottish
OL,10,Fpilot project was a "huge moment for
OL,11,Fthe SMA community", who he said have
OL,12,Fbeen campaigning for newborn screening
OL,13,Ffor a decade.
OL,15,FHe added: "With all three treatments
OL,16,Fnow routinely available through NHS
OL,17,FScotland alongside newborn screening,
OL,18,Fthe future for anyone diagnosed with
OL,19,FSMA is very different compared to
OL,20,Ftheir peers who were diagnosed
OL,21,Fsymptomatically."
OL,26,@rD@UOUsD@RO]wD@KOU
